{"tid":1810630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"貼近的平行線","createTime":"2020-01-04T05:02:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T05:02:01.000Z","uid":76678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"55eb5d9e3ad9b42f3a71c4705d4b67ebf4ace792","tid":1810630,"uid":76678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:02:01.000Z","msg":"［重甜］是咁的，我中出咗我以前個學生。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1663960\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1663960</a><br />\n<br />\n「我只知道，我與她的關係，就像兩條貼近的平行線。<br />\n<br />\n平行線的定義，就是兩條一直延伸卻永不相交的直線，無論它們有多麼接近，不會相交就是其本質。<br />\n<br />\n千萬不要去奢望它們會有相遇的一天。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}